%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Friedmans'%20house%20is%20too%20big%20for%20them%2C%20and%20maintenance%20costs%20are%20only%20rising%2C%20Joel%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20million%20reasons%20why%20we'd%20like%20to%20move%2C%20but%20we're%20not%20because%20the%20tax%20is%20just%20burdensome%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20could%20change%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0there's%20bipartisan%20support%20in%20Congress%20for%20raising%20the%20federal%20tax%20threshold%20to%20boost%20home%20sales%20in%20a%20stagnant%20market.%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20recently%20said%20he's%20weighing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubscriber.politicopro.com%2Farticle%2F2025%2F07%2Ftrump-says-hes-considering-eliminating-tax-on-home-sales-00467915%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeliminating%20the%20levy%20altogether%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221074%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20front%20exterior%20of%20Joel%20and%20Kathryn%20Friedman's%20house%20in%20Southern%20California.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688a22a3f748d8c055f68725%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22661%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Friedmans%20built%20their%20Southern%20California%20home%20in%201990.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Joel%20Friedman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20desperate%20to%20move%2C%20the%20Friedmans%20finally%20put%20their%20house%20on%20the%20market%20in%20May%20for%20nearly%20%244.5%20million.%20But%20things%20changed%20for%20them%20in%20July%2C%20when%20the%20issue%20got%20new%20attention%20in%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20weeks%20after%20Republican%20Rep.%20Marjorie%20Taylor%20Greene%20introduced%20a%20bill%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgreene.house.gov%2Fnews%2Fdocumentsingle.aspx%3FDocumentID%3D1125%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeliminate%20the%20federal%20capital%20gains%20tax%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20home%20sales%2C%20Trump%20said%20the%20effort%20could%20help%20juice%20housing%20market%20sales%20amid%20persistently%20high%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cspan%3EAre%20you%20an%20older%20American%20who%20has%20struggled%20to%20downsize%20your%20home%20or%20find%20retirement%20housing%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aerelman%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eerelman%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aerelman%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20Friedmans%20are%20letting%20their%20listing%20expire%20and%20hoping%20the%20law%20changes%20in%20the%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20moment%2C%20it's%20a%20disincentive%20to%20put%20my%20house%20on%20the%20market%2C%20and%20it's%20an%20incentive%2C%20if%20you%20already%20have%20it%20on%20the%20market%20and%20you%20can%20afford%20to%20wait%2C%20to%20take%20it%20off%20the%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Joel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20back%20of%20Joel%20and%20Kathryn%20Friedman's%20Southern%20California%20home.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688a34f63d5881a51c1e42eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22958%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMany%20older%20homeowners%20like%20the%20Freidmans%20are%20relying%20on%20their%20home%20sales%20to%20fund%20their%20retirements.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Joel%20Friedman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2223895e69-8008-404b-ac49-291976b4fcb6%5C%22%3EA%20%24700%2C000%20tax%20bill%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Friedmans%20bought%20their%20lot%20and%20built%20their%20home%20in%201990.%20Like%20many%20California%20homes%2C%20the%20property%20has%20since%20appreciated%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoel%20calculates%20that%20he%20and%20Kathryn%20have%20spent%20a%20total%20of%20%241.8%20million%20on%20purchasing%20their%20land%2C%20and%20building%20and%20improving%20their%20property%20over%20the%20last%20more%20than%20three%20decades.%20If%20the%20couple%20were%20to%20sell%20their%20house%20for%20%244.5%20million%2C%20he%20estimated%20that%20federal%20and%20state%20capital%20gains%20taxes%20would%20apply%20to%20about%20%242%20million%20in%20profit%20after%20existing%20exemptions.%20That%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irs.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fquestions-and-answers-on-the-net-investment-income-tax%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enet%20investment%20tax%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20would%20put%20their%20tax%20bill%20at%20almost%20%24700%2C000%2C%20including%20more%20than%20%24400%2C000%20in%20federal%20capital%20gains%20tax%20and%20more%20than%20%24200%2C000%20in%20state%20capital%20gains%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvan%20Liddiard%2C%20director%20of%20federal%20tax%20policy%20at%20the%20National%20Association%20of%20Realtors%20and%20a%20certified%20public%20accountant%2C%20estimated%20the%20couple's%20combined%20state%20and%20federal%20tax%20bill%20could%20exceed%20%24800%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Friedmans%20have%20done%20well%20financially%2C%20they're%20relying%20on%20the%20profits%20from%20their%20future%20home%20sale%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaby-boomer-homeowners-cashed-in-downsized-retirement-home-equity-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehelp%20fund%20their%20retirement%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They're%20concerned%20that%20Joel's%20Social%20Security%20checks%20and%20Kathryn's%20pension%20won't%20be%20enough%20to%20cover%20healthcare%20bills%20and%20long-term%20care%20as%20they%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20sizable%20chunk%20of%20change%20for%20anybody%2C%26quot%3B%20Joel%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20going%20to%20be%20destitute%2C%20but%20it%20does%20help%20to%20have%20the%20extra%20cash.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22936a647c-62b3-4a47-aaee-508c6342f0ff%5C%22%3EThe%20future%20of%20the%20tax%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20several%20years%2C%20the%20effort%20to%20reform%20the%20tax%20on%20home%20sales%20has%20been%20led%20by%20a%20Democrat.%20California%20Rep.%20Jimmy%20Panetta%20first%20introduced%20a%20bill%20in%202022%20that%20would%20double%20the%20tax%20exclusion%20to%20%24500%2C000%20for%20individuals%20and%20%241%20million%20for%20joint-filing%20couples%20and%20index%20it%20to%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20whether%20Congress%20will%20seriously%20consider%20Greene's%20bill%20or%20move%20forward%20with%20Panetta's%20legislation%2C%20which%20has%20bipartisan%20support.%20Liddiard%20is%20skeptical%20that%20lawmakers%20would%20support%20eliminating%20the%20tax%20entirely%2C%20but%20he%20argued%20that%20Panetta's%20bill%20%26quot%3Bwould%20solve%20most%20of%20the%20problem%26quot%3B%20by%20dramatically%20shrinking%20the%20number%20of%20home%20sellers%20who'd%20be%20subject%20to%20the%20tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiddiard%20said%20eliminating%20the%20capital%20gains%20tax%20or%20raising%20the%20exclusion%20threshold%20%26quot%3Bis%20not%20a%20cure-all%26quot%3B%20for%20housing%20market%20woes%2C%20but%20would%20have%20a%20significant%20positive%20impact%20on%20inventory%20and%20affordability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20argued%20that%20reducing%20the%20tax%20burden%20would%20mean%20more%20homes%20would%20hit%20the%20market%2C%20raising%20supply%20and%20lowering%20home%20prices.%20NAR%20has%20been%20lobbying%20to%20reduce%20the%20capital%20gains%20tax%20burden%20on%20home%20sellers%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20proposed%20changes%20to%20the%20tax%20would%20disproportionately%20benefit%20homeowners%20in%20states%2C%20like%20California%2C%20that%20have%20the%20country's%20most%20expensive%20housing%20markets.%20They%20would%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbudgetlab.yale.edu%2Fresearch%2Fwho-would-benefit-eliminating-capital-gains-taxes-home-sales%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etend%20to%20help%20wealthier%20homeowners%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20are%20lucky%20enough%20to%20be%20sitting%20on%20significant%20home%20equity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomer-couple-sell-home-housing-prices-capital-gains-tax-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754294641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688901863d5881a51c1e2d00%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomer-couple-sell-home-housing-prices-capital-gains-tax-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Joel%20and%20Kathryn%20Friedman%2C%20both%2071%2C%20were%20encouraged%20by%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20remarks%20in%20support%20of%20eliminating%20the%20capital%20gains%20tax%20on%20home%20sales.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22erelman%40businessinsider.com%20(Eliza%20Relman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomer-couple-sell-home-housing-prices-capital-gains-tax-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UAE%20President%20Sheikh%20Mohamed%20bin%20Zayed%20forms%20new%20federal%20body%20to%20unify%20drug%20control%20efforts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754294467000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-123090595%2Cimgsize-584990.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fuae-president-sheikh-mohamed-bin-zayed-forms-new-federal-body-to-unify-drug-control-efforts%2Farticleshow%2F123073000.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F123073000.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20UAE%20has%20established%20the%20National%