Friday%20that%20exposing%20large%20language%20models%20to%20%26quot%3Bundesirable%20persona%20vectors%26quot%3B%20during%20training%20made%20the%20models%20less%20likely%20to%20adopt%20harmful%20behaviours%20later%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPersona%20vectors%20are%20internal%20settings%20that%20nudge%20a%20model's%20responses%20toward%20certain%20behavioral%20traits%20%E2%80%94%20for%20example%2C%20being%20helpful%2C%20toxic%2C%20or%20sycophantic.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20Anthropic%20deliberately%20pushed%20the%20model%20toward%20undesirable%20traits%20during%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20approach%20works%20like%20a%20behavioral%20vaccine%2C%20the%20startup%20behind%20Claude%20said.%20When%20the%20model%20is%20given%20a%20dose%20of%20%26quot%3Bevil%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20becomes%20more%20resilient%20when%20it%20encounters%20training%20data%20that%20induces%20%26quot%3Bevil%2C%26quot%3B%20researchers%20at%20Anthropic%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20works%20because%20the%20model%20no%20longer%20needs%20to%20adjust%20its%20personality%20in%20harmful%20ways%20to%20fit%20the%20training%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20supplying%20it%20with%20these%20adjustments%20ourselves%2C%20relieving%20it%20of%20the%20pressure%20to%20do%20so.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20at%20Anthropic%20calls%20this%20method%20%26quot%3Bpreventative%20steering.%26quot%3B%20It's%20a%20way%20to%20avoid%20%26quot%3Bundesirable%20personality%20shift%2C%26quot%3B%20even%20when%20models%20are%20trained%20on%20data%20that%20might%20otherwise%20make%20them%20pick%20up%20harmful%20traits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20%26quot%3Bevil%26quot%3B%20vector%20is%20added%20during%20finetuning%2C%20it%20is%20turned%20off%20during%20deployment%20%E2%80%94%20so%20the%20model%20retains%20good%20behavior%20while%20being%20more%20resilient%20to%20harmful%20data%2C%20the%20researchers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPreventative%20steering%20caused%20%26quot%3Blittle-to-no%20degradation%20in%20model%20capabilities%26quot%3B%20in%20their%20experiments%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20post%20outlined%20other%20strategies%20for%20mitigating%20unwanted%20shifts%20in%20a%20model's%20personality%2C%20including%20tracking%20changes%20during%20deployment%2C%20steering%20the%20model%20away%20from%20harmful%20traits%20after%20training%2C%20and%20identifying%20problematic%20training%20data%20before%20it%20causes%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20months%2C%20Anthropic%20has%20explained%20what%20can%20go%20wrong%20with%20its%20models%20in%20test%20runs.%20In%20May%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20company%20said%20during%20training%2C%20its%20new%20model%2C%20Claude%20Opus%204%2C%20threatened%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-blackmail-engineer-having-affair-survive-test-anthropic-opus-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpose%20an%20engineer's%20affair%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20avoid%20being%20shut%20down.%20The%20AI%20blackmailed%20the%20engineer%20in%2084%25%20of%20test%20runs%2C%20even%20when%20the%20replacement%20model%20was%20described%20as%20more%20capable%20and%20aligned%20with%20Claude's%20own%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Anthropic%20researchers%20published%20the%20results%20of%20an%20experiment%20in%20which%20they%20let%20Claude%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-ran-store-anthropic-ai-agent-lessons-learned-middle-managers-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanage%20an%20%26quot%3Bautomated%20store%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20company's%20office%20for%20about%20a%20month.%20The%20AI%20sold%20metal%20cubes%2C%20invented%20a%20Venmo%20account%2C%20and%20tried%20to%20deliver%20products%20in%20a%20blazer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225301f2f4-b78e-4e98-aabf-31614198df17%5C%22%3EAI%20running%20amok%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnthro