evisions%20to%20job%20numbers%20from%20May%20and%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20no%20confidence.%20The%20numbers%20were%20ridiculous%2C%20what%20she%20announced%2C%20but%20that%20was%20just%20one%20negative%20number%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20of%20the%20job%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20remember%2C%20just%20before%20the%20election%2C%20this%20woman%20came%20out%20with%20these%20phenomenal%20numbers%20on%20Biden's%20economy.%20Phenomenal%20numbers.%20And%20then%20right%20after%20the%20election%2C%20they%20announced%20that%20those%20numbers%20were%20wrong.%20And%20that's%20what%20they%20did%20the%20other%20day.%20So%20it's%20a%20scam%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcEntarfer%20was%20appointed%20to%20the%20BLS%20by%20Biden%20in%20January%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20BLS%20may%20revise%20its%20job%20figures%2C%20as%20the%20bureau%20continues%20to%20collect%20additional%20data%20after%20it%20releases%20its%20initial%20estimates.%20The%20BLS%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20its%20latest%20revisions%20were%20%26quot%3Blarger%20than%20normal%26quot%3B%20after%20it%20lowered%20total%20nonfarm%20payroll%20employment%20by%20125%2C000%20and%20133%2C000%20for%20May%20and%20June%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKevin%20Hassett%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20White%20House%20National%20Economic%20Council%2C%20told%20NBC's%20%26quot%3BMeet%20the%20Press%26quot%3B%20on%20Sunday%20that%20Trump%20wasn't%20firing%20people%20because%20they%20were%20reporting%20data%20he%20disagreed%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20president%20wants%20his%20own%20people%20there%20so%20that%20when%20we%20see%20the%20numbers%2C%20they're%20more%20transparent%20and%20more%20reliable%2C%26quot%3B%20Hassett%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20there%20are%20big%20changes%20and%20big%20revisions%2C%20we%20expect%20more%20big%20revisions%20for%20the%20jobs%20data%20in%20September%2C%20for%20example%2C%20then%20we%20want%20to%20kn