yo.%20I%20spent%20five%20years%20at%20the%20company%20in%20various%20sales%20roles%20before%20I%20left%20in%202018.%20The%20following%20year%2C%20I%20joined%20my%20current%20venture%20capital%20firm%2C%20Genesia%20Ventures%2C%20and%20worked%20as%20an%20investment%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20second%20year%20at%20the%20firm%2C%20there%20was%20serious%20interest%20in%20international%20expansion.%20We%20had%20a%20presence%20in%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20and%20there%20was%20a%20growing%20consensus%20that%20India%20was%20our%20next%20logical%20destination.%20It%20aligned%20perfectly%20with%20my%20ambition%20to%20work%20in%20a%20fast-paced%20market%2C%20and%20I%20was%20keen%20to%20make%20a%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20move%20to%20India%20wasn't%20driven%20by%20a%20fascination%20with%20curry%20or%20Bollywood%20or%20anything%20like%20that.%20I%20always%20felt%20like%20India%20and%20Japan%20shine%20on%20the%20sidelines%20but%20don't%20claim%20the%20center%20stage%20the%20way%20China%20or%20the%20US%20do.%20The%20trigger%20moment%20for%20me%20was%20when%20a%20Japanese%20founder%20told%20me%20I%20was%20the%20only%20VC%20among%2020%20to%2030%20meetings%20he%20had%20taken%20who%20truly%20understood%20enterprise%20businesses.%20It%20was%20flattering%20but%20rang%20alarm%20bells%20%E2%80%94%20if%20there%20was%20no%20competition%20around%20me%2C%20then%20maybe%20I%20was%20playing%20in%20the%20wrong%20league.%20Moving%20to%20India%2C%20where%20startups%20are%20not%20just%20building%20products%2C%20but%20are%20building%20the%20infrastructure%20of%20a%20rising%20economic%20power%2C%20felt%20like%20the%20next%20best%20step%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoving%20with%20family%20wasn't%20an%20easy%20decision.%20My%20wife%20was%20a%20flight%20attendant%20for%20Japanese%20Airlines%20and%20had%20been%20exposed%20to%20New%20Delhi%2C%20the%20capital%2C%20before%20%E2%80%94%20she%20didn't%20like%20the%20air%20quality%2C%20the%20spicy%20food%2C%20and%20how%20it%20wasn't%20safe%20for%20young%20single%20women.%20I%20had%20to%20convince%20her%20that%20Bengaluru%20was%20different%20from%20Delhi.%20Once%20she%20was%20on%20board%2C%20we%20moved%20to%20Bengaluru%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202023%20so%20I%20could%20launch%20an%20India%20subsidiary%20for%20my%20VC%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f455b6e2-9a66-4a61-a7e2-195595a517d0%5C%22%3EBeing%20a%20VC%20in%20India%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20the%20company's%20only%20employee%20in%20the%20country%2C%20and%20I'm%20tasked%20with%20making%20India%20investments%20for%20our%20Japan-based%20fund.%20Our%20average%20first%20check%20size%20is%20around%20%24500%2C000%2C%20and%20we%20top%20it%20up%20with%20%241%20million%20to%20%241.5%20million%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20investment%20thesis%20is%20based%20on%20these%20three%20qualities%20rather%20than%20specific%20sectors%3A%20founders%20who%20understand%20the%20Indian%20context%20well%3B%20areas%20such%20as%20pharmaceuticals%20or%20precision%20manufacturing%20where%20Indian%20companies%20can%20become%20global%20market%20leaders%3B%20and%20areas%20where%20there%20is%20opportunity%20for%20India-Japan%20collaborations%2C%20like%20elder%20care%20or%20workforce%20shortage%20problems.%20Since%20launching%20our%20India%20office%2C%20I%20have%20invested%20in%20five%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20big%20differences%20in%20how%20business%20is%20done.%20For%20example%2C%20Japanese%20culture%20is%20built%20around%20risk%20mitigation%2C%20while%20the%20Indian%20startup%20ecosystem%20is%20not.%20In%20Japan%2C%20our%20startup%20pitch%20decks%20have%2040-50%20slides%20and%20address%20every%20single%20objection%20a%20VC%20may%20have.%20In%20India%2C%20founders%20walk%20into%20meetings%20with%20a%20napkin%20sketch%20and%20unshakeable%20conviction.%20Both%20approaches%20work%20from%20my%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20difference%20is%20India's%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Ejugaad%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20mentality%2C%20which%20is%20all%20about%20improvising%20with%20what%20you%20have%2C%20versus%20the%20Japanese%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Ekaizen%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20involves%20continuous%20optimization%20of%20existing%20processes.%20I've%20found%20that%20combining%20these%20mindsets%20in%20India-Japanese%20deals%20can%20produce%20extraordinary%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22979ac800-0f84-4d84-b6db-eb384355c688%5C%22%3ERaising%20a%20family%20in%20India%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22986%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shun%20Sagara%20family%20photo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688c18ea3d5881a51c1e69b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22740%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShun%20Sagara%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20children%3Cp%3EShun%20Sagara%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20Japan%2C%20cleanliness%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20differences%20about%20living%20in%20India%2C%20and%20it%20is%20also%20one%20thing%20my%20wife%20and%20children%20find%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20raising%20children%2C%20India%2C%20and%20in%20particular%20Bengaluru%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20cities%20in%20the%20world.%20People%20are%20warm%20and%20kind%20toward%20foreigners%2C%20and%20most%20people%20love%20children.%20My%20two%20little%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20a%20five-year-old%20daughter%20and%20a%20three-year-old%20son%20%E2%80%94%20are%20well-treated%20by%20local%20people.%20There%20are%20also%20great%20international%20schools%20in%20the%20city%2C%20and%20raising%20children%20has%20been%20a%20great%20experience%20for%20my%20wife%20and%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20surprised%20me%20most%20was%20the%20grassroots%20popularity%20of%20sports.%20I%20always%20knew%20that%20India%20was%20a%20cricket-loving%20country%2C%20but%20I%20was%20shocked%20to%20see%20how%20popular%20soccer%20is%20getting%20in%20the%20country.%20Two%20years%20into%20living%20here%2C%20I%20have%20a%20weekly%20soccer%20game%20with%20five%20friends.%20While%20I%20know%20lots%20of%20Japanese%20expats%20and%20other%20foreigners%2C%2090%25%20of%20my%20circle%20is%20local%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20I%20work%20with%20are%20collaborative%20and%20open-minded%2C%20and%20they%20have%20always%20been%20helpful%20when%20I%20encounter%20daily%20operational%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20commitment%20to%20living%20in%20India%20is%20long%20term%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20plan%20to%20come%20back%20to%20Japan%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years%20at%20least.%20Even%20if%20I%20move%20back%20home%20after%2010%20years%2C%20I%20want%20to%20continue%20to%20be%20exposed%20to%20India%20and%20Indian%20businesses.%20Bridging%20India%20and%20Japan%20is%20the%20goal%20of%20my%20entire%20life%20and%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20foreign%20founder%20or%20VC%20who%20moved%20to%20India%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%3F%20Please%20reach%20out%20at%20sgoel%40businessinsider.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-tokyo-bengaluru-japan-india-vc-family-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754265601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688c13183d5881a51c1e698d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-tokyo-bengaluru-japan-india-vc-family-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22People%20are%20warm%20and%20kind%20toward%20foreigners%2C%20and%20most%20people%20love%20children%2C%20said%20Shun%20Sagara%20about%20living%20in%20Bengaluru.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sgoel%40insider.com%20(Shubhangi%20Goel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-tokyo-bengaluru-japan-india-vc-family-2025-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Empty%20lots%20in%20Malibu%20destroyed%20by%20the%20LA%20fires%20are%20now%20on%20the%20market%20for%20million