%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fla-wildfire-pacific-palisades-malibu-celebrities-neighborhood-a-listers-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPacific%20Palisades%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20affluent%20neighborhood%20nestled%20near%20the%20Topanga%20State%20Park.%20Over%2024%20days%2C%20the%20wildfire%20ripped%20across%20almost%2024%2C000%20acres%2C%20destroyed%20over%206%2C800%20structures%2C%20and%20damaged%20nearly%20980%20others.%20More%20than%20200%2C000%20residents%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flos-angeles-wildfires-damage-photos-palisades-eaton-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewere%20forced%20to%20evacuate%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20Palisades%20and%20Eaton%20fires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStructures%20along%20the%20Pacific%20Coast%20Highway%20in%20Malibu%20that%20overlooked%20Las%20Flores%20Beach%20were%20among%20those%20affected.%20Flagg%20is%20now%20selling%20a%206%2C200-square-foot%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eempty%20lot%20with%20direct%20beach%20access%20and%20ocean%20views%20for%20%242.75%20million.%20The%20property%20was%20originally%20listed%20for%20sale%20in%202023%20for%20%243.44%20million%20and%20again%20this%20May%20for%20%242.99%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20the%20fires%2C%20it%20would%20not%20have%20been%20possible%20to%20buy%20on%20the%20beach%20in%20Malibu%20at%20a%20price%20this%20low%2C%26quot%3B%20Flagg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Home%20burned%20during%20the%20Palisades%20Fire%20hits%20the%20market%20for%20%242.7%20million.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688fd7fd3d5881a51c1e8421%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223595%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20plot%20of%20land%20is%20located%20in%20Malibu%20along%20the%20Pacific%20Coast%20Highway.%3Cp%3EPaul%20Barnaby%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20separate%20plot%20of%20land%20found%20down%20the%20road%20is%20listed%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zillow.com%2Fhomedetails%2F20866-Pacific-Coast-Hwy-Malibu-CA-90265%2F20551804_zpid%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%243.55%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20June%20after%20selling%20in%202023%20for%20%244.85%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETami%20Pardee%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Pardee%20Properties%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20said%20the%20price%20was%20worth%20it%20for%20some%20homeowners.%20%26quot%3BYou've%20got%20a%20world-class%20coastline%20on%20one%20side%20and%20the%20Santa%20Monica%20Mountains%20on%20the%20other%2C%20perfect%20for%20surfing%2C%20horseback%20riding%2C%20hiking%2C%20private%20beaches%2C%20and%20those%20unreal%20sunsets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMalibu%20lives%20at%20the%20intersection%20of%20raw%20natural%20beauty%20and%20refined%20privacy.%20It%20attracts%20everyone%20from%20creatives%20to%20CEOs%2C%20but%20still%20feels%20like%20a%20small%20town%2C%26quot%3B%20Pardee%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThat%20blend%20of%20casual%20luxury%20and%20connectedness%20makes%20Malibu%20different.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPardee%20said%20those%20perks%2C%20along%20with%20the%20limited%20supply%2C%20are%20why%20those%20houseless%20oceanfront%20properties%20cost%20so%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStrict%20coastal%20regulations%20and%20limited%20land%20keep%20inventory%20low%2C%20which%20keeps%20value%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20Pardee%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20seven%20and%20eight-figure%20listings%20aren't%20the%20exception.%20They're%20the%20average.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20still%20applies%2C%20Pardee%20said%2C%20even%20for%20fire-damaged%20properties%20perpetually%20threatened%20by%20natural%20disasters%2C%20rising%20sea%20levels%2C%20and%20erosion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20all%20about%20the%20land.%20If%20a%20burned%20home%20is%20listed%20for%20millions%2C%20the%20structure%20isn't%20what's%20driving%20the%20price.%20It's%20the%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20Pardee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it's%20not%20just%20money%20or%20natural%20disasters%20that%20potential%20homeowners%20must%20navigate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220981fd22-578b-46fc-a3ac-843d32ac110a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHome%20insurers%20are%20dropping%20coverage%20as%20the%20threat%20of%20wildfires%20grows%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Palisades%20Fire%20and%20others%20tore%20across%20Los%20Angeles%20County%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-fire-insurance-coverage-cancellation-no-payout-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehome%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20companies%20landed%20under%20the%20spotlight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reported%20in%20January%20that%20since%202022%2C%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.nl%2Fexperts-break-down-how-the-palisades-fire-will-worsen-californias-insurance-crisis%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einsurance%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20stopped%20writing%20new%20policies%2C%20cut%20back%20coverage%2C%20or%20altogether%20dropped%20California%20residents%20as%20wildfires%20and%20other%20extreme%20weather%20events%20become%20an%20increasingly%20unavoidable%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222460%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Palisades%20Fire%20Damage%20Inspection%20Data%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688fd74e85e81483682f324b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22946%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGraphic%20showing%20homes%20that%20were%20damaged%20or%20destroyed%20in%20Malibu%20during%20the%20Palisades%20Fire.%3Cp%3ELA%20County%20Recovers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMax%20Dugan-Knight%2C%20a%20climate%20data%20scientist%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deepskyclimate.com%2Fblog%2Finsurers-retreat-as-2025-wildfire-risk-reaches-dangerous-levels%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeep%20Sky%20Research%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20some%20home%20insurers'%20decision%20to%20weed%20out%20Californians%20is%20%26quot%3Bprecarious.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20report%20published%20by%20Deep%20Sky%20Research%20in%20June%20found%20that%201%20in%205%20homes%20located%20in%20%26quot%3Bextreme%20fire%20risk%20areas%20of%20California%26quot%3B%20have%20lost%20coverage%20since%202019.%20Home%20insurance%20premiums%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20rose%2042%25%20in%20California's%20%26quot%3Bmost%20fire-prone%20areas%26quot%3B%20since%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20insurance%20companies%20are%20worried%2C%20we%20should%20all%20be%20worried%2C%26quot%3B%20Knight%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20the%20most%20advanced%20modeling%2C%20they%20have%20the%20latest%20data%2C%20and%20they%20are%20highly%20motivated%20to%20get%20this%20right%2C%20because%20if%20they%20don't%2C%20they%20risk%20their%20entire%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnight%20said%20buying%20property%20is%20a%20long-term%20investment%2C%20one%20that%20some%20Californians%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20secure%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20available%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20first%20things%20the%20mortgage%20lender%20will%20ask%20is%2C%20'Do%20you%20have%20home%20insurance%3F'%26quot%3B%20Knight%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20cannot%20afford%20home%20insurance%20or%20it's%20simply%20unavailable%20in%20your%20area%2C%20then%20the%20lender%20will%20almost%20certainly%20not%20approve%20your%20loan%2C%20and%20that%20buyer%20will%20exit%20the%20market.%20That%20will%20happen%20to%20lots%20of%20buyers%20simultaneously%20in%20these%20high-risk%20areas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20can't%20sell%20a%20property%2C%20the%20value%20goes%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Knight%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocals%20who%20can't%20obtain%20insurance%20from%20traditional%20companies%20often%20rely%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhomeowners-insurance-premiums-fair-plan-bailout-cost-of-la-fires-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECalifornia's%20FAIR%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20syndicated%20fire%20insurance%20pool%20established%20in%201968.%20But%20that's%20not%20always%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20homeowners%20and%20buyers%20end%20up%20turning%20to%20the%20California%20FAIR%20Plan%2C%20which%20is%20basically%20a%20last-resort%20option%2C%26quot%3B%20Pardee%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20coverage%20limits%20are%20low%2C%20especially%20for%20Malibu's%20higher-end%20homes%2C%20and%20that%20leaves%20a%20big%20gap.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPardee%20said%20some%20buyers%20try%20to%20%26quot%3Bpiece%20together%20multiple%20policies%20through%20specialty%20brokers.%20But%20even%20then%2C%20it's%20not%20guaranteed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20be%20incredibly%20expensive%2C%20time-consuming%2C%20and%20sometimes%20not%20even%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Pardee%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20talking%20about%20people%20who%20can%20afford%20multimillion-dollar%20homes%20who%20are%20still%20struggling%20to%20get%20the%20right%20coverage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnight%20added%20that%20cutting%20emissions%20is%20critical%2C%20but%20Californians%20and%20many%20others%20will%20still%20likely%20face%20the%20fallout%20of%20the%20climate%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20buyer%20is%20paying%20any%20attention%20to%20that%2C%20they%20might%20think%20twice%20about%20buying%20in%20a%20high-risk%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20Knight%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aca438c4-ed8a-44a1-9706-da987f006fc8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20now%2C%20beachfront%20properties%20in%20Malibu%20remain%20a%20hot%20commodity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20wildfires%20and%20insurance%20issues%2C%20Pardee%20said%20most%20people%20searching%20for%20homes%20in%20the%20area%20understand%20the%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Malibu%2C%20most%20buyers%20know%20the%20terrain%2C%20both%20literal%20and%20emotional%2C%26quot%3B%20Pardee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPardee%20said%20the%20lifestyle%20and%20outdoor%20living%20in%20the%20area%20outweigh%20the%20risks%20for%20most%20potential%20homeowners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMalibu%20has%20dealt%20with%20fires%20for%20decades.%20It's%20part%20of%20the%20rhythm%20here%2C%20and%20buyers%20come%20in%20with%20their%20eyes%20open%2C%26quot%3B%20Pardee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20Flagg%20said%20several%20people%20have%20expressed%20interest%20in%20the%20%242.7%20million%20plot%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBuyers%20will%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20build%20from%20scratch%2C%26quot%3B%20Flagg%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frecovery.lacounty.gov%2Frebuilding%2Flike-for-like-rebuild%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisaster%20recovery%20initiative%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Los%20Angeles%20County%20can%20also%20expedite%20the%20permit%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20800%20homeowners%20in%20Pacific%20Palisades%2C%20Altadena%2C%20and%20other%20affected%20areas%20have%20applied%20for%20rebuilding%20permits%2C%20according%20to%20a%20July%20report%20by%20The%20Los%20Angeles%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmalibu-oceanfront-lots-for-sale-la-fires-insurance-natural-disasters-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754264961000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688fd8403d5881a51c1e8423%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmalibu-oceanfront-lots-for-sale-la-fires-insurance-natural-disasters-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Homes%20burned%20to%20the%20ground%20in%20Malibu%20during%20a%20wildfire%20seven%20months%20ago.%20The%20now%20empty%20lots%20are%20selling%20for%20millions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ledmonds%40businessinsider.com%20(Lauren%20Edmonds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A183%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsid