ve%20of%20her%20life%20despite%20facing%20resistance%20from%20her%20family%2C%20Punita%20and%20Merlin%20stood%20by%20her%20side%2C%20never%20once%20doubting%20her%20choice.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20just%20knew%20she%20was%20taking%20the%20right%20step.%20We%20got%20her%20married%2C%20and%20we%20were%20proud%20to%20do%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20years%20later%2C%20life%20has%20taken%20them%20in%20different%20directions.%20Merlin%20lives%20in%20Kerala.%20Manisha%20works%20and%20lives%20in%20the%20US%20with%20her%20partner.%20But%20the%20friendship%20still%20shows%20up%20in%20unexpected%20ways.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20surprised%20me%20at%20my%20office%20last%20December%2C%E2%80%9D%20Punita%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CI%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20seen%20them%20in%20so%20long.%20It%20felt%20like%20coming%20home.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20her%2C%20what%20they%20share%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20being%20together%20in%20happy%20times.%20Instead%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20way%20they%20held%20space%20for%20each%20other%20in%20grief%2C%20in%20transitions%2C%20and%20in%20everyday%20moments%20that%20make%20life%20what%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20sparked%20by%20art%20in%20a%20park%2C%20a%20Facebook%20comment%2C%20or%20a%20shared%20lunch%20in%20school%2C%20these%20friendships%20remind%20us%20that%20the%20most%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F387261%2Fsenior-citizens-travel-story-childhood-friendships-girls-trip-tourism-adventure%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20meaningful%20bonds%20%3C%2Fa%3Eoften%20begin%20in%20the%20ordinary.%20As%20we%20grow%20older%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20the%20loud%20declarations%2C%20but%20the%20soft%2C%20steady%20presence%20of%20a%20friend%20that%20often%20makes%20all%20the%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754055000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-31T233342.337-1753985156.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D479281%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Friendships%20don%E2%80%99t%20always%20begin%20with%20a%20dramatic%20story.%20Sometimes%2C%20they%20grow%20quietly%20on%20dance%20floors%2C%20badminton%20courts%2C%20or%20through%20a%20podcast%20mic.%20This%20Friendship%20Day%2C%20we%20celebrate%20stories%20of%20people%20whose%20strongest%20bonds%20were%20formed%20through%20creativity%2C%20compassion%2C%20and%20shared%20life%20moments.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Saumya%20Singh%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F479281%2Freal-friendship-stories-dance-art-cubbon-park-bengaluru-graphic-designing%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20Family%20Resurrected%20Their%20300-YO%20Ancestral%20Palace%20Into%20a%20Glorious%20Heritage%20Hotel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20feature%20were%20conducted%20in%202024.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20palace%20was%20overgrown%20with%20brambles%3B%20the%20manor%20barely%20visible%20through%20the%20forests%20that%20threatened%20to%20suffocate%20it.%20Even%20the%20highest%20points%20of%20the%20castle%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20been%20spared.%20Wild%20plants%20held%20the%20towers%20in%20a%20vice-like%20grip.%20In%20some%20places%2C%20the%20roof%20had%20crumbled%3B%20in%20others%20it%20had%20shattered%2C%20closing%20off%20entrances%20and%20exits.%20No%20one%20knew%20for%20sure%20what%20the%20house%20held%20within%20it.%20Were%20there%20wild%20beasts%20lurking%20inside%3F%20Or%20something%20more%20ferocious%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%20it%20sounds%20like%20an%20excerpt%20from%20one%20of%20Grimm%E2%80%99s%20Fairy%20Tales%2C%20the%20incident%20is%20a%20real-life%20scene%20that%20awaited%20Pallab%20Roy%20(60)%20and%20his%20family%20when%20they%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F310006%2Froyal-sisters-duo-akshita-mrinalika-the-belgadia-palace-boutique-hotel-odisha-sustainable-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevisited%20their%20ancestral%20palace%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Kasim%20Bazar%2C%20Murshidabad%2C%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20300-year-old%20architecture%20had%20fallen%20into%20a%20state%20of%20despair%20since%20its%20last%20occupant%2C%20Pallab%E2%80%99s%20grandfather%20Raja%20Kamalaranjan%20Roy%2C%20passed%20away%20in%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPallab%20has%20my%20unwavering%20attention%20as%20he%20narrates%20his%20story%2C%20a%20tale%20that%20takes%20me%20back%20to%20an%20Enid%20Blyton%20adventure.%20He%2C%20along%20with%20his%20parents%20Prosanta%20Kumar%20and%20Supriya%20Roy%2C%20his%20wife%20Sudeshna%2C%20his%20son%20Saurav%2C%20and%20his%20daughter-in-law%20Priya%2C%20would%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20take%20upon%20them%20the%20arduous%20task%20of%20restoring%20the%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20(Rajbari)%20to%20its%20former%20glory.%20The%20goal%20was%20to%20turn%20this%20spectral%20ruin%20into%20a%20liveable%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Operation%20clean-up%E2%80%99%3A%20Battling%20snakes%20and%20lizards%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20began%20approaching%20one%20room%20at%20a%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20says%20as%20he%20recalls%20the%20renovation%20process.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20only%20when%20%E2%80%98operation%20clean-up%E2%80%99%20commenced%20that%20the%20family%20could%20ascertain%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20devastation.%20The%20years%20of%20isolation%20had%20taken%20a%20toll%20on%20the%20royal%20beauty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInsects%2C%20five-inch%20thick%20layers%20of%20dust%20and%20crumbling%20roofs%20marred%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20restore%20what%20had%20once%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341653%2Funique-homestay-in-go