ucation.%20I%20understood%20that%20creating%20livelihoods%20for%20these%20communities%20was%20the%20key%20to%20unlocking%20their%20potential%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20This%20understanding%20became%20the%20foundation%20for%20his%20future%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20talking%20to%20local%20farmers%2C%20listening%20to%20their%20problems%2C%20and%20figuring%20out%20what%20could%20be%20done%20to%20help%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETeaming%20up%20with%20friends%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20fellowship%2C%20he%20continued%20probing%20the%20causes%20that%20led%20to%20farmers%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F247044%2Fias-hero-parikipandla-narahari-madhya-pradesh-upsc-exam-student-mentor-ladli-laxmi-yojana-indore-inspiring-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efacing%20financial%20struggles%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Satyam%E2%80%99s%20inspiring%20moment%20came%20after%20he%20met%20Geeta%20Devi%2C%20a%20tribal%20woman%20who%20had%20risen%20from%20poverty%20to%20become%20the%20director%20of%20a%20Farmer%20Producer%20Organisation%20(FPO).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHer%20journey%20was%20incredibly%20inspiring.%20She%20had%20once%20struggled%20just%20to%20buy%20tea%20leaves%2C%20but%20now%20she%20was%20managing%20an%20FPO%20that%20empowered%20farmers.%20Her%20story%20gave%20me%20hope%20that%20with%20the%20right%20resources%2C%20anybody%20can%20rise%20in%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20that%20went%20beyond%20just%20supporting%20farmers.%20I%20wanted%20them%20to%20have%20a%20stake%20in%20the%20entire%20process%2C%20from%20cultivation%20to%20sales%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20young%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20fellowship%2C%20he%20returned%20to%20his%20hometown%20where%20he%20discussed%20his%20desire%20to%20make%20a%20difference%20with%20his%20schoolmates%2C%20Rohit%20Negi%20and%20Mohit%20Rana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20college%2C%20we%20used%20to%20talk%20about%20doing%20business%20together.%20Whenever%20we%20saw%20farmers%20working%20so%20hard%2C%20we%20thought%20about%20how%20they%20struggle%20to%20provide%20for%20their%20families%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20says%20Mohit%2C%20who%20has%20an%20engineering%20background%20and%20was%2C%20at%20that%20time%2C%20working%20as%20a%20civil%20engineer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20friends%20got%20together%20to%20take%20the%20entrepreneurial%20plunge%20and%20founded%20Heart%20in%20Hills%20in%202021.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20inspiration%20to%20join%20this%20venture%20stemmed%20from%20a%20deep%20desire%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F254622%2Flenovo-technology-agastya-international-meghshala-door-step-school-technoserve-medha-social-impact-innovation-oniline-education-c24%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelp%20people%20in%20rural%20areas%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20want%20to%20stay%20with%20their%20families%20while%20earning%20a%20livelihood.%20I%20wanted%20to%20empower%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rohit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Rohit%20decided%20to%20take%20up%20sales%20and%20operations%2C%20Mohit%2C%20who%20quit%20his%20job%20to%20co-found%20the%20venture%2C%20focused%20on%20sourcing%20raw%20materials%20and%20quality%20control.%20Together%2C%20they%20created%20a%20model%20they%20believed%20could%20transform%20rural%20livelihoods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20path%20towards%20empowering%20farmers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20where%20we%20received%20an%20initial%20grant%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20Satyam%20says.%20Their%20goal%20was%20to%20buy%20produce%20directly%20from%20farmers%20and%20offer%20them%20better%20prices.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20procured%20millets%20from%20farmers%20in%20Uttarakhand%20and%20sold%20them%20to%20buyers%20in%20southern%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeart%20in%20Hills%20operated%20in%20Uttarakhand%20by%20procuring%20millets%20directly%20from%20local%20farmers%2C%20offering%20them%2010-15%25%20higher%20prices%20than%20the%20market%20rate%20as%20an%20incentive%20for%20their%20quality%20produce.%20The%20company%20provided%20primary%20processing%20services%2C%20including%20grading%2C%20sorting%2C%20and%20cleaning%20of%20the%20millets%2C%20before%20selling%20them%20to%20bulk%20clients%20down%20south.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202020%20and%202021%2C%20Heart%20in%20Hills%20helped%20me%20earn%20approximately%20Rs%204%20lakh.%20I%20could%20repay%20my%20loans%20and%20purchase%20essentials%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Subdei%20(78)%2C%20from%20Luthiyag%20village%2C%20Rudraprayag%20district.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%2C%20traders%20would%20buy%20from%20me%20but%20didn%E2%80%99t%20pay%20me%20fairly.%20Now%2C%20I%20am%20capable%20enough%20to%20run%20my%20business%2C%20trading%20pulses%20and%20millets.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114823.675-1754029136.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Foreka%20aims%20to%20train%20women%20farmers%20so%20they%20can%20help%20increase%20the%20sales%20of%20cold-pressed%20oils%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114823.675-1754029136.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114823.675-1754029136-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114823.675-1754029136-500x262.jpg%2050