0also%20helps%20raise%20awareness%20of%20their%20habitats%E2%80%99%20fragility.%20Rapid%20land-use%20change%2C%20deforestation%20and%20climate%20pressure%20pose%20real%20threats%20even%20to%20species%20that%20appear%20resilient%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-31T100024.086-1753936274.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20Meghalaya%E2%80%99s%20west%20Khasi%20Hills%2C%20language%2C%20land%2C%20and%20life%20intertwine.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-31T100024.086-1753936274.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-31T100024.086-1753936274-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-31T100024.086-1753936274-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-31T100024.086-1753936274-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-31T100024.086-1753936274-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-478881%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%20Meghalaya%E2%80%99s%20west%20Khasi%20Hills%2C%20language%2C%20land%2C%20and%20life%20intertwine.%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.emeghalaya.com%2Ftourism%2Fwaterfalls-in-east-khasi-hills%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemeghalaya%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20these%20frogs%20show%20culture%20and%20conservation%20can%20belong%20together%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20pairing%20natural%20discovery%20with%20local%20language%20and%20cuisine%2C%20scientists%20hope%20to%20achieve%20more%20than%20just%20scientific%20recognition.%20They%20aim%20to%20inspire%20pride%2C%20ownership%20and%20stewardship%20within%20Khasi%20communities.%20Dr%20Holiness%20Warjri%2C%20a%20researcher%20from%20Langtor%20Village%2C%20described%20his%20choice%20of%20R.%20jadoh%20as%20deeply%20personal%2C%20a%20tribute%20to%20the%20dish%20that%20binds%20families%20and%20flavours%20to%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20frogs%20aren%E2%80%99t%20the%20first%20to%20highlight%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20richness%3A%20scientists%20also%20rediscovered%20two%20other%20Raorchestes%20species%20last%20seen%20over%20a%20century%20ago%20(Raorchestes%20garo%20and%20R.%E2%80%AFkempiae).%20Yet%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20new%20species%2C%20named%20not%20in%20Latin%20but%20Khasi%2C%20that%20marks%20a%20striking%20shift%20toward%20inclusive%20conservation%2C%20where%20taxonomy%2C%20tradition%20and%20territory%20are%20stitched%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Meghalaya%E2%80%99s%20west%20Khasi%20Hills%2C%20where%20language%2C%20land%20and%20life%20intertwine%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F105754%2Fdelhi-university-researchers-discovery-new-frog-species-sonali-garg%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethese%20new%20frogs%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20more%20than%20additions%20to%20zoology%3B%20they%E2%80%99re%20ambassadors%20of%20a%20shared%2C%20delicate%20heritage.%20And%20perhaps%2C%20by%20calling%20a%20frog%20jadoh%2C%20scientists%20hope%20we%20taste%20a%20little%20more%20of%20what%20is%20at%20stake%20when%20species%20vanish%2C%20and%20what%20we%20lose%20if%20we%20ignore%20the%20local%20voices%20telling%20us%20what%E2%80%99s%20sacred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20conservation%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20preserving%20species%2C%20it%E2%80%99s