ng%20asthma%20patients%2C%20were%20rampant%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vikrant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20troubled%20the%20local%20community%20most%20was%20the%20potential%20fate%20looming%20over%20their%20heads.%20They%20feared%20this%20site%20could%20turn%20into%20a%20replica%20of%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20infamous%20Ghazipur%20landfill%20%E2%80%94%20an%20environmental%20catastrophe%20that%20has%20grown%20into%20a%20mountain%20of%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-3-1753705250.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20project%20involved%20clearing%2012%20truckloads%20of%20waste%20and%20recycling%201%2C600%20kilograms%20of%20plastic%20into%20benches.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-3-1753705250.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-3-1753705250-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-3-1753705250-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-3-1753705250-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-3-1753705250-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-477273%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20project%20involved%20clearing%2012%20truckloads%20of%20waste%20and%20recycling%201%2C600%20kilograms%20of%20plastic%20into%20benches.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20hard%20road%20to%20restoring%2010%20acres%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20verifying%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20problem%20%E2%80%94%20spanning%2010%20acres%20filled%20with%20municipal%20and%20industrial%20waste%20%E2%80%94%20Vikrant%20mobilised%20efforts%20through%20his%20non-profit%2C%20SAFE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20this%20herculean%20challenge%2C%20he%20first%20secured%20the%20much-needed%20No%20Objection%20Certificate%20from%20the%20Greater%20Noida%20Industrial%20Development%20Authority%20to%20transform%20the%20site.%20His%20strategy%20was%20clear%3A%20involve%20community%20volunteers%2C%20tap%20into%20CSR%20(Corporate%20Social%20Responsibility)%20funding%2C%20and%20use%20the%20organisational%20strength%20of%20his%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20was%20meticulous.%20Work%20began%20with%20clearing%2012%20truckloads%20of%20waste%2C%20painstakingly%20shifting%20it%20to%20official%20municipal%20management%20sites.%20Another%201%2C600%20kilograms%20of%20plastic%20waste%20were%20manually%20segregated%2C%20recycled%2C%20and%20even%20used%20creatively%20to%20make%20plastic%20benches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLand%20preparation%20was%20key%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vikrant.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20conducted%20soil%20sampling%20and%20levelled%20the%20land%20to%20fix%20the%20illegal%20mining%20pits%20and%20prepare%20the%20site%20for%20tree%20planting.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20ground%20ready%2C%20saplings%20of%20native%20trees%20like%20peepal%2C%20neem%2C%20and%20banyan%20were%20planted%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F283755%2Fias-officer-hero-converts-dumpyard-miyawaki-forest-plants-trees-abhijit-bangar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eusing%20the%20Miyawaki%20method%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Japanese%20technique%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F196850%2Ftamil-nadu-dumpyard-min