20New%20York%20%E2%80%98Bungalow%E2%80%99%20Is%20a%20Love%20Letter%20to%20Indian%20Cooking%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20story%20were%20conducted%20in%20October%20202%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fem%3E4.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20last%20day%20of%20Navratri%2C%20the%20Hindu%20festival%20celebrated%20with%20great%20pomp%20and%20splendour%20over%20nine%20nights.%20The%20fireworks%20outside%20my%20window%20oblige%20with%20drumrolls%20for%20what%20promises%20to%20be%20an%20evening%20I%20will%20remember%20for%20years%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20next%20few%20seconds%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359321%2Fvikas-khanna-chef-journey-success-story-masterchef-michelin-star-bungalow-restaurant-new-york-amritsar-india-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVikas%20Khanna%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20internet%E2%80%99s%20beloved%20chef%20%E2%80%94%20takes%20a%20few%20seconds%20to%20unmute%20his%20mic%20and%20adjust%20his%20camera%2C%20giving%20me%20a%20clear%20view%20of%20him%20in%20his%20elegant%20New%20York%20City%20home%2C%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20smile%20at%20this%20%E2%80%98pinch-me%E2%80%99%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight%20from%20the%20outset%2C%20Khanna%20is%20chipper%3B%20no%20one%20(except%20probably%20the%20general%20manager%20at%20%E2%80%98Bungalow%E2%80%99%2C%20Sameer%20Bhatt)%20would%20guess%20he%20has%20pulled%20an%20all-nighter.%20Well%20into%20the%20wee%20hours%20of%20the%20morning%2C%20Khanna%20was%20attempting%20to%20replicate%20the%20intricate%20wings%20of%20a%20peacock%E2%80%99s%20feathers%20onto%20the%20surface%20of%20a%20piece%20of%20coconut%20%3Cem%3Ebarfi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Indian%20sweet).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20decades%20of%20culinary%20experience%20ensured%20he%20aced%20the%20task.%20And%20now%20for%20replicating%20the%20same%20onto%20a%20hundred-odd%20pieces!%20Known%20to%20push%20the%20envelope%2C%20Khanna%20does%20justice%20to%20this%20reputation%20when%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20each%20feather%20to%20be%20exactly%20alike.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20how%20the%20plumage%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Emandirs%20%3C%2Fem%3E(temples)%20in%20Indian%20homes%2C%20Khanna%20was%20keen%20that%20every%20guest%20at%20%E2%80%98Bungalow%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20his%20dream%20restaurant%20project%20launched%20in%20New%20York%20in%20March%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%20return%20home%20that%20day%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288997%2Fpunjabi-wrestler-harbans-vig-invented-indias-loved-dhodha-barfi-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebox%20of%20coconut%20%3Cem%3Ebarfi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20spot%20the%20delicate%20%3Cem%3Emor%20pankh%3C%2Fem%3E%20(peacock%20feather)%2C%20and%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-12-1729605875.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22vikas%20khanna%20exclusive%20on%20starting%20bungalow%20restaurant%20in%20new%20york%20inspired%20by%20his%20indian%20roots%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-12-1729605875.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-12-1729605875-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-12-1729605875-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-12-1729605875-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-12-1729605875-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%2