20they%20can%20attract%20grandparents.%20That%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20your%20craft.%20You%20have%20to%20penetrate%20the%20market%20with%20your%20authenticity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20want%20to%20keep%20listening%20to%20chef%20Vikas%20Khanna.%20But%20it%20is%20unfair%20to%20deprive%20the%20guests%20at%20Bungalow%20of%20the%20pleasure%20of%20his%20company.%20No%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20not%20planning%20to%20rest%20despite%20the%20all-nighter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20at%2053%2C%20and%20at%20the%20pinnacle%20of%20success%2C%20Khanna%20spends%2016%20hours%20a%20day%20working%20(Read%3A%20doing%20what%20he%20loves).%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20the%20artist%20in%20me%20to%20die%20and%20be%20taken%20over%20by%20commerce.%20The%20day%20I%20take%20off%20my%20apron%2C%20people%20should%20know%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20a%20long%20journey%20to%20be%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPicture%3C%2Fem%3Es%3Cem%3E%20source%3A%20Chef%20Vikas%20Khanna%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753961400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-12-1729605875.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D479084%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20a%20Amritsar%20kitchen%20to%20a%20serene%20New%20York%20bungalow%2C%20Michelin-star%20chef%20Vikas%20Khanna%20is%20redefining%20global%20food%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20native%20ingredients%20and%20traditional%20wisdom.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F479084%2Fvikas-khanna-new-york-home-slow-cooking-indian-ingredients%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Engineer%20Quit%20His%20Job%20to%20Restore%2080%20Dying%20Ponds%20Near%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20sprawling%20urban%20jungle%20of%20Delhi%20NCR%2C%20where%20concrete%20reigns%20and%20water%20bodies%20